---
title: Kidney Bean Chilli with cauliflower rice and coriander garnish
description: Chilli is by nature a hearty sort of dish, and this kidney bean chilli certainly lives up to that reputation. Filled with fibre and protein, and with a lower carb rice alternative it's not only hearty but healthy too!
